videos.description: Michigan State's defense comes up with a nice steal, and Gabe Brown gets the ball for the dunk. On the ensuing possession, Aaron Henry comes up with the block, and Brown once again gets the ball for a good score and the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Great MSU defense leads to pair of nice Brown scores) 2019/12/14

videos.headline: Great MSU defense leads to a pair of nice Brown scores

videos.description: Tom Izzo's son Steven hauls in a defensive rebound. Brock Washington gets the ball and lobs it up to Malik Hall for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Izzo's rebound leads to a Hall dunk) 2019/12/14

videos.headline: Izzo's rebound leads to a Hall dunk
